Collaborate & Create Imagery Powered by AI

Facet empowers you to alter images in new ways. Experience the power of AI – full content awareness, and smart recommendations that allow you to iterate and experiment faster and better. It’s all on a cloud-based platform that lets your whole team collaborate smoothly.

Unify Everything

Match all your imagery project-wide. Facet can gracefully apply edits to wildly different images. Save effort and easily give your whole project a consistent look & feel. Make big changes quickly, without sacrificing nuance.

Try Your Hand

See Through Things

Control your content. Facet recognizes everything in a photo. You have the power to declutter, remove or replace anything. It knows what skin looks like, so color profiles are balanced, and subjects can match new environments.

Start Experimenting

Share Your Vision

Collaborate smoothly with your entire team. Facet enables everyone to be involved in the process. Experiment together, and communicate better. Create powerful Patterns that can be shared and applied by anyone.

For All Types, Styles & Scales

No matter what kind of professional you are, or what workflow you prefer, Facet fits right in. It’s designed with a diverse range of professionals in mind. We want to empower everyone from makers to marketing managers to influencers to photographers and beyond.

Test it out

See it to believe it.

Facet is iterative by its nature. Every time you use it, your photos will improve. Likewise we’re constantly rolling out new features and functionalities.
